description: Aspose.Diagram is a class library for working with Microsoft Visio files. It allows developers to create new diagrams and work with VSD, VSDX, VSTX, VSSX, VSS, VST, VSX, VTX, VDW and VDX files on ASP.NET web applications, web services and Windows applications. It allows you to open files and manipulate the elements of the diagram, from lines and fills, to more complex elements, and then export to VDX, VSX,VSDX,VSSX,VSTX, VTX, XPS, HTML, SVG, SWF, XAML, image or PDF formats.
releaseNotes:
This release introduces the features, enhancements,task and bug fixes as detailed below:
   
   New Features   
   DIAGRAMNET-51081-Add support to modify the individual gradient stop
   
   Enhancements
   DIAGRAMNET-51071-The gradient color of the shape is not being preserved on saving in VSDX
   DIAGRAMNET-51075-The gradient color of circle shape is not shown on saving in VSDX
   DIAGRAMNET-51109-Improvement to set the gradient stop properties
     
    Bugs  
   DIAGRAMNET-51054-Incomplete rendering of the dynamic connectors on converting a VSD to PDF
   DIAGRAMNET-51073-Incomplete rendering of the circle shape on saving in VDX
   DIAGRAMNET-51077-Incomplete rendering of the circle shape on saving in VDX    
   DIAGRAMNET-51098-VSD to PDF export - the extra white space is generated on the left side of the drawing
   DIAGRAMNET-51099-VSD to HTML export - the extra white space is generated on the left side of the drawing
   DIAGRAMNET-51100-VSD to SVG export - the background color of container turns into black
   DIAGRAMNET-51101-Can't group shapes second time in a Visio Drawing page
   DIAGRAMNET-51102-The group shape becomes invisible on adding circular shapes in a VSDM
   DIAGRAMNET-51103-Page.AddShape method shows an invalid error on adding a dynamic connector
   DIAGRAMNET-51105-Missing an embedded excel on converting a VSD to PDF
   DIAGRAMNET-51114-Missing an embedded excel on converting a VSD to PDF
   DIAGRAMNET-51117-The text items in the bullets are not aligned well on converting a VSD to PDF
summary: Aspose.Diagram is a class library for working with Microsoft Visio files.
title: Aspose.Diagram for .NET
